// import 'src/App.css';
import React from 'react';
import Card from '@mui/material/Card';
import CardContent from '@mui/material/CardContent';
import { CardActionArea } from '@mui/material';
import { Button, Grid, Grow, Typography } from '@mui/material';
import Box from '@mui/material/Box';
import Stack from '@mui/material/Stack';
import '../style/leader.css';
import '../style/cards.css'
import Leaderboard from '../pages/leaderboard';
import Trajectory from '../pages/trajectory';



function Home() {
    
    return (
        <Box component="main" sx={{flexGrow: 1, p:3}}>
            <Grid>
              <Grid item xl={1}>
                <Stack spacing={2} direction="row">
                  <Card className='cards'>
                    <CardActionArea>
                      <CardContent>
                        <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="div">
                        Statistic
                        </Typography>
                        <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                        </Typography>
                      </CardContent>
                    </CardActionArea>
                  </Card>

                  <Card className='cards'>
                    <CardActionArea>
                      <CardContent>
                        <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="div">
                          Best Score
                        </Typography>
                        <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">

                        </Typography>
                      </CardContent>
                    </CardActionArea>
                  </Card>

                  <Card className='cards'>
                    <CardActionArea>
                      <CardContent>
                        <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="div">
                          Fastest Time
                        </Typography>
                        <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                  
                        </Typography>
                      </CardContent>
                    </CardActionArea>
                  </Card>

                  <Card className='cards'>
                    <CardActionArea>
                      <CardContent>
                        <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="div">
                          Model Name
                        </Typography>
                        <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                        </Typography>
                      </CardContent>
                    </CardActionArea>
                  </Card>
                </Stack>
              </Grid>
            </Grid>

            {/* The code below is where the leaderboard will be located */}
            <Box height={20} />
            <Grid container spacing={2}>
              <Grid item xs={8}>
                <Card sx={{height: 60 + "vh"}} className='cards-two'>
                    <CardContent>
                      <Leaderboard /> {/* Calls the leaderboard.js which incorporates leaderboard.jsx*/}
                    </CardContent>
                </Card>
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={4}>
                <Card sx={{height: 60 + "vh"}} className='cards-two'>
                 
                    <CardContent>
                    <Trajectory />
                    </CardContent>
                 
                </Card>
              </Grid>
            </Grid>
          </Box>
        
    );
}

export default Home;
